description:
Is forgiveness a one-time thing, or is it something we do over and over? 

This #cut from the video, Forgiveness [How Do We Learn to Forgive?] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FLAnaq2KfMk, explains exactly what forgiveness means, and why it is so vital to learn how to forgive. Oftentimes, our definition of forgiveness can be quite different from Gods. 

Watch the video to learn what the Bible says about forgiveness and how we can learn to forgive someone who has hurt us.
